t of new markets and the setting up of new offices or M&As globally. The Ideal Candidate should possess the following: Possesses a Degree in Accountancy/ Finance. ACCA or CPA. Has at least 15 - 20 years of work experience, with prior experience of reporting directly to the BOD. Is articulate, has strong business acumen and is a charismatic leader A hands-on leader with demonstrated skill in leading, building and nurturing finance teams to support business strategies and goals. Resourceful, a team player and able to work with people at all levels and from different cultures and backgrounds. Commercial awareness partnered with a strategic and entrepreneurial mindset Willingness to be based in Singapore. Thank you for your interest in joining us. We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. ", 
